msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../C/Cinderella-Book.rst:9
msgid ""
"[CMU] *Introduction to Automata Theory, Languages, and Computation*\\, by "
"John Hopcroft and Jeffrey Ullman, (Addison-Wesley, 1979). So called because "
"the cover depicts a girl (putatively Cinderella) sitting in front of a Rube "
"Goldberg device and holding a rope coming out of it. On the back cover, the "
"device is in shambles after she has (inevitably) pulled on the rope. See "
"also :ref:`book-titles`\\."
msgstr ""
"[CMU] John HopcroftとJeffrey Ullmanによる『Introduction to Automata Theory, "
"Languages, and Computation』(Addison-Wesley、1979年)。表紙にRube "
"Goldberg装置の前に座り、そこから出ているロープを握る少女(おそらくシンデレラ)が描かれていることからこう呼ばれます。裏表紙では、彼女が(必然的に)ロープを引いた後で装置がめちゃくちゃになっています。\\"
" :ref:`book-titles`\\ も参照。"
